results.name: Permutation of natural numbers induced by the Catalan bijection gma082351 acting on the parenthesizations encoded by A014486/A063171.
link: A. Karttunen, Gatomorphisms (with the complete Scheme source)
Index entries for signature-permutations induced by Catalan automorphisms
program: (Scheme functions implementing this automorphism on list-structures:)
(define (gma082351! s) (cond ((not (pair? s)) s) ((not (pair? (car s))) s) ((not (pair? (cdr s))) (robl! (swap! s))) (else (robl! s))))
(define (robl! s) (let ((ex-car (car s))) (set-car! s (cddr s)) (set-cdr! (cdr s) ex-car) (swap! (cdr s)) (swap! s) s))
(define (swap! s) (let ((ex-car (car s))) (set-car! s (cdr s)) (set-cdr! s ex-car) s))
